{"about_the_game":"Hello everyone! We are Mechland, a small development team of two members. This is our brand new side-scrolling souls-like game, Black Spire!<br><br>Our initial goal in designing this game was to create a \u2018Souls game for everyone\u2019, so we simplified our basic game control to just attack and roll. The character will move on itself. Attack and parry share the same button. We hope this design can further streamline combat controls so that the transition between attack and defense can be more seamless. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/newq1.gif?t=1702712519\" /><br><br>Of course, you can do far more than this. You can experience so much more in this adventure, getting equipment and accessories and learning a wide array of moves and magics that can be really helpful when you are in a pinch. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/newq2_1.gif?t=1702712519\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/newq2_2.gif?t=1702712519\" /><br><br>Please take your time to explore Black Spire and hone your skills. Strategize your combat style however you like, and slay every opponent that stands in your way! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/newq3.gif?t=1702712519\" /><br><br>You\u2019ll also encounter many characters along the journey. Listen to their stories and decide whether you want to help them. It might not always be easy, but you might reap the rewards of friendship in unexpected ways. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/newq4.gif?t=1702712519\" /><br><br>Like any Souls game, boss fights are meant to be challenging. These elite enemies will try everything to stop you. And you can only go higher over their dead bodies. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/newq5.gif?t=1702712519\" /><br><br>Slay your enemies to reap the rewards, and uncover the dark secrets behind Black Spire. We hope you enjoy our game and have lots of fun!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Black Spire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/da6a52f580729b299ead3e8ad860d7fd020338ff.jpg"},{"name":"Honor of Annular Vale","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/50524a46a43cd9fea3485cefb497bb0f846c1583.jpg"},{"name":"Collector of Wristlets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/5f35485c287a091499471e2072dbdcca942ff227.jpg"},{"name":"Master of Sword Skills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/00025719be0d2fcc75f121f1ded71a8bf2500a05.jpg"},{"name":"Master of Magic Skills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/1ef64aa016123da69da6af02a210318dcba16009.jpg"},{"name":"Supreme Armor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/5f0b6242299903cdf95a076d9ab11f6159ae9382.jpg"},{"name":"Black Spire Centurion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/99dc3034a547e898716f8205ec51b7f8943fb52b.jpg"},{"name":"Lady Sylv","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/018d8978c7e2f659ed75b4ee6f5248a753eb1f96.jpg"},{"name":"Molten Abomination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/1d7a847e057eaad0e88f96b5faae32f5ca78e716.jpg"},{"name":"The Crazy Bielsa","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352120/61cd662d52acd376d387f212882e987c67a2c768.jpg"}],"total":22},"background":"ht